&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 1974 hindi movie , produced by j.k. kapur and directed by tapan sinha , the film stars dilip kumar , saira banu , aparna sen and om prakash . it was a remake of a bengali version called &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; which was released in 1970 , directed by tapan sinha , with the same lead pair in the cast .